\ip \bd ?Pah t…ôm…ôte naoa u?\bd* Aposol Pol t…ôm…ôte naoa u.  
\ip \bd ?T…ôm…ôte tatuw…®n k…ôm pah?\bd* T…ôm…ôte tatuw…®n k…ôm Timoti. K…ôn in molkeike m…ôm…ô ilat m…®n …ôp…ôh e nim…ôfak r…ôha Efesas, m…ôm…ô okotafin. Afin e ‚ÄúNamnus…ôn ∆èku…ôk…®r R…ôha Naoa u 1 Timoti‚Äù o n…®tun…ôn m…ôm…ô Timoti in pah.  
\ip \bd ?N…ômeg…ôh…ôn tahro nulan nian t…ôm…ôte?\bd* Nian kapman r…ôha Rom task…ôl…®m Pol …ôp…ôh Rom, in t…ôs…ôtat…®g…ôn e kalapus, m…ôto in t…ôm…ôtat…®g e r…ôhan kit nim…ô, k…ôn mopael m…®n k…ômotat…®g ilat min motehm m…ôm…ô in ot…ôsag…®m…ôn. Namnun japta r…ôha W…ôk M…®n tat…ôghat-in nian m…®n …ôh. K…ôn …ômun kapman t…ômahl-iar…ôp in, k…ôn taliw…ôk …ôm m…ôtan o nup k…ôiu. M…ôto roiu …ôh, t…®nuw…®n m…®n e kalapus …ôp…ôh Rom, k…ôn kalapus …ôh in t…ôrat ik…®n pahrien. Naoa r…ôha W…ôk M…®n t…ôs…ôghat-in…ôn nian …ôh, naoa t…®nol namnun r…ôk…®s. Kalapus …ôh in t…ôt…ôp ik…®n, k…ôn ti…ôk…®s o net…ômim o nuw…®n…ôn m…ôtag-p…ôn-in. Luk …ôm ilau min. Pol t…ômolkeike m…ôm…ô Timoti otuwa mehm m…ôto-inu in r…ôhan fren w…®r. K…ôn in molkeike m…ôm…ô Timoti in ot…ôm…®k naoa m…®n r…ôhan.  
\ip \bd ?T…ôm…ôte naoa u o naka?\bd* Pol t…ôm…®tun m…ôm…ô ot…ôsuw…ôh…ôn kohamnu in t…®m…®s. Tol n…ôhlan, in t…ôm…ôte naoa u o n…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn…ôn nim…ôfak e nelm…® net…ôm-iasol p…®s…®n m…®n neen tahmen e Timoti. Nian i…ôk…®s m…®n koatuwa o nim…ôfak, k…ôn Pol in tolkeike m…ôm…ô Timoti ot…ôtask…ôl…®m Namnus…ôn T…ôw…®r, k…ôn mat…ôtul …ôskas…®k e nahat…ôt…ô…ôn r…ôhan, k…ôn m…ôs…ôgin…ôn n…ôn-iar…ôp…ôn Namnus…ôn T…ôw…®r, k…ôn in ot…ôtul mat…®p o n…ôto…ôn nahm…ô…ôn e n…®p…ôt…®n ok…ôm…ô n…ôrat…ôn otuwa.  
\c 1  
\s1 Pol t…ôm…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm Timoti  
\m
\v 1 Io Pol, u io aposol kit r…ôha Kristo Iesu, it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…®t…ôpun r…ôk…®s io m…ôm…ô r…ôhan, k…ôn mahl-ipa io m…ôm…ô ek…ôn-iar…ôp r…ôhan n…ôni…ôk…®s…ôn r…ôha n…ômeg…ôh…ôn lil…®n e Kristo Iesu.  
\v 2 Iat…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm ik Timoti, n…ôt…®k it…ôm iakolkeike p…®k ik. P…ôs Uhg…®n Tata ne Kristo Iesu r…ôhatat I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô okuawte-in r…ôhalau n…ôw…®r…ôn, ne nas…ôkitun…ôn, ne n…ôm…ôlinu…ôn k…ôm ik.\x - \xo 1:2 \xt W…ôk 16:1; 1 Tim 1:2 \x*   
\s1 Pol t…ôm…®l…ôs-ip…ôr n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôha Timoti  
\p
\v 3 Nian rafin, lap…®n ne lenian, iat…ôfak ron ik, k…ôn mat…ôn tagkiu k…ôm Uhg…®n ron ik. K…ôn iatol w…ôk r…ôhan tahmen-p…ôn …ôm e t…®p…®k m…®n, k…ôn ek…®tun m…ôm…ô nol…ôn rat kit t…ôsat…®g…ôn lak.\x - \xo 1:3 \xt W…ôk 23:1 \x*  
\v 4 N…®kik tatu…ôh nahui n…ômt…ôm, k…ôn iakolkeike p…®k m…ôm…ô ek…ôplan m…®n ik p…ôs n…®kik otagien.  
\v 5 N…®kik tatu…ôh nahat…ôt…ô…ôn pahrien r…ôham it…ôm tahmen-p…ôn …ôm e nahat…ôt…ô…ôn it…ôm t…ômaup…ôn m…ôtat…®g e r…ôham pipi Lois ne r…ôham mama Iunis, k…ôn ek…®tun m…ôm…ô roiu in t…®n…ôtat…®g lam.\x - \xo 1:5 \xt W…ôk 16:1 \x*  
\v 6 K…ôn tol n…ôhlan, iat…ôn m…®n k…ôm ik m…ôm…ô onakelel n…®g…ôm r…ôha n…ôsan…ôn…ôn it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ômos-ip…®n…ô o nol…ôn r…ôhan w…ôk. Uhg…®n t…ômos-ip…®n…ô n…ôsan…ôn…ôn …ôh nian em…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn nelm…ôk mat…ôfak-p…®n…ô lam.\x - \xo 1:6 \xt 1 Tim 4:14 \x*  
\v 7 Ol w…ôk e n…ôsan…ôn…ôn …ôh, m…ôto-inu Uhg…®n t…ôsos-ipam…ôn k…ôm kitat n…®kin r…ôha n…ôg…®n…ôn, m…ôto t…ômos-ipa n…®kin r…ôha n…ôsan…ôn…ôn, ne n…®kin r…ôha nolkeike…ôn, ne n…®kin it…ôm tatol nol…ôn m…®n it…ôm in t…®tun m…ôm…ô kot…ôtuat…®p.\x - \xo 1:7 \xt Rom 8:15 \x*   
\p
\v 8 K…ôn in…ôh, …ôsaul…®s-in…ôn o n…ôn-iar…ôp…ôn I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, k…ôn …ôsaul…®s-in…ôn io it…ôm etat…®g e kalapus o n…ôrg…®n. M…ôto e n…ôsan…ôn…ôn it…ôm Uhg…®n tatos-ip…®n…ô k…ôm ik, n…ôk…ôike mol m…ôm…ô io ne, it…ôm iat…ôto nahm…ô…ôn o namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r.  
\v 9 Uhg…®n t…ômosmeg…ôh kitat k…ôn maun-in kitat m…ôm…ô kitat okotuwa r…ôhan m…®n net…ômim it…ôm kotasim, k…ôn t…ôm…ôsol…ôn o nat kit it…ôm kitat k…ômotol, m…ôto in t…ômol e r…ôhan at…®p n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn, ne n…ôw…®r…ôn. Nian Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôsol…ôn …ôh n…ôtueint…ôn ne, m…ôto in t…ôm…ôl…ôh…ôu r…ôk…®s nalp…ôkau…ôn m…ôm…ô in otawte-in r…ôhan n…ôw…®r…ôn k…ôm kitat e Kristo Iesu,\x - \xo 1:9 \xt Efes 2:8-9; Taet 3:5 \x*  
\v 10 m…ôto roiu, in t…ômol …ôp n…ôw…®r…ôn …ôh k…ôm kitat e nuwam…ôn r…ôha Iosmeg…ôh r…ôhatat, Kristo Iesu. K…ôn Kristo t…ôm…ôr…ôk…®n n…®m…®s…ôn ne r…ôhan n…ôsan…ôn…ôn, k…ôn t…ômasi…ôg…ôp…®n n…ômeg…ôh…ôn u namnun t…®k…ô, k…ôn kitat koatehm e namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r.\x - \xo 1:10 \xt Hip 2:14 \x*  
\v 11 K…ôn Uhg…®n t…ôm…®t…ôpun io m…ôm…ô io i…ôghat, ne aposol, ne i…ôg…ôtun o namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r …ôh.\x - \xo 1:11 \xt 1 Tim 2:7 \x*  
\v 12 Tol n…ôhlan iat…ôto p…®k nahm…ô…ôn ron u ik…®n-u e kalapus. M…ôto esaul…®s-in…ôn, m…ôto-inu ek…®tun m…ôm…ô pah u iatahat…ôt…ô lan, k…ôn m…®tun w…®r m…ôm…ô in t…®tun nehm w…®r…ôn nat naka it…ôm in t…ôm…ôl…ôh…ôu-pa e nelm…ôk o namnun nian.\f + \fr 1:12 \ft Suat…®p p…®s…®n o n…ôuhlin…ôn ves 12b: ‚Äúk…ôn m…®tun w…®r m…ôm…ô in t…®tun nehm w…®r…ôn nat naka it…ôm io em…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn e nelm…®n o namnun nian.‚Äù\f*   
\p
\v 13 ∆èt…ôu-p…ôn …ôm suat…®p r…ôha n…ôg…ôtun…ôn u t…ôtuat…®p it…ôm em…ôn k…ôm ik, k…ôn ol nat u e nahat…ôt…ô…ôn ne nolkeike…ôn e Kristo Iesu.  
\v 14 E nasitu…ôn r…ôha Narm…®n R…ôha Uhg…®n it…ôm t…ôtat…®g e n…®kitat, k…ôn atehm w…®r nat w…®r it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn e nelm…ôm.\x - \xo 1:14 \xt 1 Tim 6:20 \x*   
\p
\v 15 N…ôk…®tun m…ôm…ô r…ôhak m…®n net…ômim …ôp…ôh Esia, ilat Fukelas ne Hermokenes, ilat rafin k…ômotag…®m r…ôk…®s motap…ôs io.   
\p
\v 16 P…ôs I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô otas…ôkitun Onesiforas ne r…ôhan m…®n, m…ôto-inu nian tep…ôt t…ôm…ôtasitu lak mat…®l…ôs-ip…ôr r…ôhak n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn. K…ôn t…ôm…ôsaul…®s…ôn m…ôm…ô em…ôtat…®g e kalapus.  
