\p
\v 8 At…ôt…ôl…®g-in Iesu Kristo u noanol r…ôha Tef…®t, k…ôn Uhg…®n t…ômosmeg…ôh in e n…®m…®s…ôn. K…ôn inu namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r iat…ôn-iar…ôp.\x - \xo 2:8 \xt Rom 1:3; 1 Kor 15:4 \x*  
\v 9 K…ôn iat…ôto nahm…ô…ôn o namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r …ôh, k…ôn n…®pahrien…ôn, k…ôm…ôlis io e sen tahmen-p…ôn m…ôm…ô io iakl…ôh kit o iohamnu it…ôm. M…ôto k…ôs…ôlis…ôn n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n.\x - \xo 2:9 \xt Efes 3:1,13; Fil 1:12-14 \x*  
\v 10 Tol n…ôhlan, iat…ôtul …ôskas…®k e nahm…ô…ôn m…®n rafin o net…ômim it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…®t…ôpun ilat, m…ôm…ô in otosmeg…ôh ilat e Kristo Iesu, k…ôn ilat okotat…®g e n…ôw…®r…ôn it…ôm t…ôhag-…ôhag r…ôha Uhg…®n, it…ôm namnun t…®k…ô.   
\p
\v 11 Inu n…ôghat…ôn tat…ôn pahrien m…ôm…ô,  
\q1 Ok…ôm…ô kotuwa kiti…ôh e Kristo e n…®m…®s…ôn r…ôhan,  
\q1 k…ôn okot…ômeg…ôh m…®n kitat min.\x - \xo 2:11 \xt 2 Kor 4:11 \x*   
