\s1 Iolw…ôk t…ôw…®r r…ôha Uhg…®n  
\p
\v 14 Nat…®mnat m…®n u, on…ôk…ôike mat…ôn mat…®s…®mat…®p lan k…ôm r…ôham m…®n net…ômim. ∆èn …ôskas…®k k…ôm ilat n…ôhlan m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúIat…ôn e n…ôrg…®n Uhg…®n m…ôm…ô it…ômat n…ôsot…ôrg…ôh…ôu…ôn o n…®p…ôt…® n…ôghat…ôn m…®n.‚Äù N…ôrg…ôh…ôu…ôn n…ôhlan t…ôsasitu…ôn e suah kit, m…ôto tat…ôr…ôk…®n …ôm net…ômim it…ôm koat…ôto.\x - \xo 2:14 \xt 1 Tim 6:4; Taet 3:9 \x*  
\v 15 Alkut …ôskas…®k m…ôm…ô on…ôkuwa iolw…ôk t…ôw…®r it…ôm nian Uhg…®n tat…ôplan r…ôham w…ôk, in t…®tun n…ôn…ôn m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú∆èw…ôh, n…ômol t…ôw…®r,‚Äù k…ôn n…ôsaul…®s…ôn o r…ôham w…ôk, m…ôto-inu nat…ôg…ôtun …ôtuat…®p n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha n…®pahrien…ôn.\x - \xo 2:15 \xt 1 Tim 4:6 \x*  
\v 16 M…ôto ap…ôs n…ôghat…ôn …ôpnap…®n m…®n …ôm it…ôm kot…ôrat m…ôsot…®siai-in…ôn Uhg…®n, m…ôto-inu net…ômim it…ôm koat…ôghat n…ôhlan, n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhalat tatuw…®n matuw…®n …ôm o nol…ôn m…®n it…ôm k…ôsot…®siai-in…ôn Uhg…®n.\x - \xo 2:16 \xt 1 Tim 4:7 \x*  
\v 17 N…ôg…ôtun…ôn r…ôhalat in tahmen-p…ôn …ôm e n…®m…ôg…ôm pien it…ôm tat…ôm…ôhal matep…ôt matol iahgin. T…ôs mil u kioal min-nulan, ilau u Haemeneus ne Faelitas,\x - \xo 2:17 \xt 1 Tim 1:20 \x*  
\v 18 it…ôm k…®nu…ômkar…ôp…ôn r…ôk…®s e suat…®p r…ôha n…®pahrien…ôn. Katu…ôn m…ôm…ô Uhg…®n t…ômol kitat kot…ômeg…ôh m…®n r…ôk…®s e n…®m…®s…ôn, k…ôn okol Uhg…®n t…ôsos-ipa m…®n…ôn n…®p…ôt…®tat wi m…®n nian Iesu tatuwa m…®n. K…ôn t…ôs mil u katu…ôr…ôk…®n nahat…ôt…ô…ôn r…ôha net…ômim neen.  
\v 19 M…ôto tol pap n…ôhlan, nim…ô it…ôm Uhg…®n tatil…ôk…®n tat…ôtul ti…ôk…®s, k…ôn t…ôm…ôte-p…ôn lan m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúI…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô t…®tun net…ôm m…®n u r…ôhan m…®n,‚Äù ne ‚ÄúNet…ôm m…®n u koat…ôn m…ôm…ô ilat net…ôm r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, okot…ôk…ôike motap…ôs nol…ôn rat m…®n.‚Äù\x - \xo 2:19 \xt Nam 16:5; Aes 52:11; Jon 10:14; 1 Kor 8:3 \x*   
\p
\v 20 ∆èt…ôl…®g-in-tu. E nim…ô r…ôha et…ôm r…ôhan naut…ô tep…ôt, plet p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n tep…ôt. K…ômol neen e iaen u kol tat…®p…®t-…®p…®t, neen e silfa, neen e n…®g, neen e n…®m…ôpt…ôn. W…ôk r…ôha neen, in w…ôk asol it…ôm kat…®siai-in. K…ôn w…ôk r…ôha neen, in w…ôk …ôpnap…®n …ôm it…ôm tol naul…®s…ôn.  
\v 21 Ok…ôm…ô suah kit tatol r…ôhan n…ômeg…ôh…ôn tatuwiwi m…ôtap…ôs nol…ôn r…ôha naul…®s…ôn, in t…®tun nol…ôn w…ôk asol it…ôm kat…®siai-in, k…ôn Uhg…®n ot…ôl…ôh…ôu kal…®n m…ôm…ô r…ôhan p…®s…®n …ôm, k…ôn mol …ôpen-…ôpen…ô m…ôm…ô otol w…ôk m…®n it…ôm kot…ôw…®r.   
\p
\v 22 Aiu muw…®n is…ôu o nol…ôn rat m…®n it…ôm tat…ôwi…ô e n…®ki net…ôm alu…ô. K…ôn …ôt…ôu-p…ôn w…®r suat…®p r…ôha nat…®mnat m…®n u: nol…ôn it…ôm t…ôtuat…®p, ne nahat…ôt…ô…ôn, ne nolkeike…ôn, ne n…ôm…ôlinu…ôn. ∆èt…ôu-p…ôn suat…®p …ôh it…ômat net…ôm m…®n u it…ôm koat…ôtap…ôh o nasitu…ôn r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô e n…®kilat it…ôm t…ôw…®r.\x - \xo 2:22 \xt 1 Tim 6:11 \x*  
\v 23 Ap…ôs mag…®m r…ôk…®s e n…ôghat…ôn alm…ôl m…®n it…ôm n…®p…ôt…®lat t…®k…ô. N…ôghat…ôn m…®n …ôh koatiuw-pa …ôm t…®m…ôht o n…ôrg…ôh…ôu…ôn.\x - \xo 2:23 \xt 1 Tim 4:7 \x*  
\v 24 Iolw…ôk r…ôha I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô, okol in t…ôs…ôrg…ôh…ôu…ôn, m…ôto in tat…ôk…ôike matol t…ôw…®r k…ôm net…ômim rafin, k…ôn ot…ôk…ôike muwa et…ôm r…ôha n…ôg…ôtun…ôn, k…ôn r…ôhan n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn kaif…ôm…ôh.  
