\m
\v 1 M…ôto on…ôk…ôike m…®tun n…ôghat…ôn u m…ôm…ô nian …ôskas…®k m…®n okotuwa iu…ôhk…®r o Namnun Nian.\x - \xo 3:1 \xt 1 Tim 4:1 \x*  
\v 2 Tol n…ôhlan m…ôto-inu, net…ômim okoat…ôt…ôl…®g-in at…®p …ôm ilat, k…ôn ilat okotolkeike p…®k m…ôni. Net…ômim okotausit, moatos-ip…ôr at…®p …ôm ilat. Ilat okot…ôn rat net…ômim ne Uhg…®n, k…ôn ilat okot…ôht n…ôwia tata ne mama, k…ôn ok…ôsot…ôn…ôn m…ôm…ô n…®kilat t…ôtagien o nat it…ôm katol k…ôm ilat, k…ôn ok…ôsot…®siai-in…ôn Uhg…®n.  
\v 3 R…ôhalat nolkeike…ôn k…ôm net…ômim ot…®k…ô, k…ôn ok…ôsotaluin…ôn n…ôrat…ôn it…ôm suah kit otol k…ôm ilat. Ilat okot…ôr…ôk…®n n…ôrg…® net…ômim. Ok…ôsot…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô…ôn e nol…ôn m…®n r…ôhalat. N…®kilat otagien …ôm o n…ôr…ôk…®n…ôn net…ômim. Okotet…ôhau nat it…ôm in t…ôw…®r.  
\v 4 Ilat k…ôut k…ôsu…ô m…®n, k…ôn okotol nat…®mnat rat neen m…ôto k…ôsot…ôt…ôl…®g-in…ôn m…ôm…ô nat naka otiet lan. K…ôn ilat okot…®l…ôs-ip…ôr at…®p ilat, k…ôn ilat okotolkeike p…®k nat…®mnat o n…ôto…ôn t…ôw…®r e n…®p…ôt…®lat, m…ôto ilat ok…ôsotolkeike…ôn Uhg…®n.  
\v 5 Okotol nol…ôn m…®n r…ôha i…ôfak m…®n m…ôm…ô net…ômim okot…ôplan, m…ôto ilat ok…ôsotolkeike…ôn m…ôm…ô n…ôsan…ôn…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n ot…ôuhlin r…ôhalat n…ômeg…ôh…ôn mol kotuwiwi. Uw…®n is…ôu o net…ôm m…®n u.\x - \xo 3:5 \xt Mat 7:15,21; Taet 1:16 \x*   
\p
\v 6 Ap…ôs …ôm ilat m…ôto-inu neen koatehm suat…®p o nuw…®n…ôn latu…ônu m…®n, k…ôn moatiuw r…ôk…®s n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôha n…®p…®tan it…ôm r…ôhalat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn t…ôs…ôskas…®k…ôn. T…ôfag…ô rat m…®n r…ôha n…®p…®tan m…®n u, in ti…ôk…®s p…®k olat, k…ôn nol…ôn rat m…®n tep…ôt it…ôm ilat koatolkeike, koatiuw-p…ôn ilat.  
\v 7 K…ôn n…®p…®tan m…®n …ôh koat…ôt…ôl…®g-in w…®r e n…ôghat…ôn m…®n rafin r…ôha net…ôm m…®n …ôh, m…ôto ko k…ôsot…®tun…ôn n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha n…®pahrien…ôn.  
\v 8 Aup…ôn ik…®n, Janes ne Jampres k…ômatioal t…®m…ôht k…ôm Moses,\f + \fr 3:8 \ft Janes ne Jampres, ilau i…ôm…®k n…ôr…®k mil r…ôha kig r…ôha Ijip.\f* k…ôn e nol…ôn kiti…ôh m…®n …ôm, net…ôm m…®n …ôh koat…ôht n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha n…®pahrien…ôn. Net…ôm m…®n u, r…ôhalat n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn t…ôrioah e nol…ôn rat m…®n, k…ôn nol…ôn r…ôha nahat…ôt…ô…ôn r…ôhalat in neiueiu…ô-…ôm…ôn.\x - \xo 3:8 \xt Eks 7:11 \x*  
\v 9 M…ôto n…ôg…ôtun eiueiu…ô…ôn r…ôhalat, ko t…ôs…ôtul…ôn tuw…ôh, m…ôto-inu net…ômim rafin okot…ôplan m…ôm…ô ilat k…ôsot…®tun…ôn nat it…ôm koat…ôghat-in, kotahmen-p…ôn …ôm e suah mil …ôh.   
\s1 N…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Pol k…ôm Timoti  
\p
\v 10 M…ôto ik, Timoti, ik n…ôm…ôt…ôu-p…ôn r…ôhak n…ôg…ôtun…ôn, ne nol…ôn r…ôha n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhak, ne nat naka it…ôm ekolkeike m…ôm…ô ekol, ne r…ôhak nahat…ôt…ô…ôn, ne nol…ôn r…ôha n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôhak it…ôm t…ôf…ôm…ôh, ne r…ôhak nolkeike…ôn, ne n…ôtul …ôskas…®k…ôn r…ôhak,  
\v 11 k…ôn n…ôk…®tun nian i…ôk…®s m…®n it…ôm koatuwa e r…ôhak n…ômeg…ôh…ôn, ne nol…ôn t…ôrat m…®n it…ôm katol lak. K…ôn n…ôk…®tun nol…ôn i…ôk…®s m…®n it…ôm k…ômol lak …ôp…ôh Antiok, ne Ikoniam, ne Listra.\x - \xo 3:11 \xt W…ôk 13:50; 14:5; 14:19\x* M…ôto I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô t…ôm…®l…ôs-ir…ôk…®s io e nat…®mnat m…®n …ôh rafin.\x - \xo 3:11 \xt Sam 34:19\x*  
\v 12 N…®pahrien…ôn, net…ômim rafin it…ôm kotolkeike m…ôm…ô okotol nol…ôn it…ôm Uhg…®n tolkeike, k…ôn motol e Kristo Iesu, net…ômim okotol t…ôrat k…ôm ilat,\x - \xo 3:12 \xt Mat 16:24; Jon 15:20; W…ôk 14:22 \x*  
\v 13 m…ôto nian kiti…ôh m…®n …ôm, nol t…ôfag…ô rat m…®n ne net…ôm r…ôha neiueiu…ô…ôn, ilat okotol nol…ôn rat motuw…®n kol it…ôm in t…ôrat ag…®n. Ilat net…ômim kateiu…ô-in ilat,\f + \fr 3:13 \ft Setan o net…ômim p…®s…®n m…®n okoteiu…ô-in ilat.\f* k…ôn ilat okoteiu…ô-in p…®k ag…®n-…ôh net…ômim.   
\p
\v 14 M…ôto ik, Timoti, onak…ôk…ôike mat…ôt…ôu-p…ôn …ôm nat…®mnat w…®r m…®n it…ôm k…ôm…ôg…ôtun ik lan it…ôm n…ôm…ôn …ôskas…®k r…ôk…®s n…®pahrien…ôn lan, m…ôto-inu ik n…ôk…®tun w…®r net…ômim it…ôm k…ômot…ôg…ôtun ik lan.  
\v 15 K…ôn nian n…ômat…ôk…ôku m…ôtoarus-pa u-roiu, n…ôm…®tun Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n it…ôm t…®tun nos-ip…ôn…ôn nenat…®g…ôn m…ôm…ô n…ôk…®tun nos…ôn n…ômeg…ôh…ôn lil…®n lan o nahat…ôt…ô…ôn e Kristo Iesu.  
\v 16 N…ôghat…ôn m…®n rafin e Naoa R…ôha Uhg…®n, k…ômot…®s…®-p…ôn …ôm e nohl…® Uhg…®n, k…ôn koatasitu etat. Koat…ôg…ôtun kitat, moat…ôni…ôp nol…ôn rat m…®n r…ôhatat, moat…ôg-…ôtuat…®p-in kitat, k…ôn moat…ôg…ôtun kitat e nol…ôn m…®n it…ôm kot…ôtuat…®p.\x - \xo 3:16 \xt Rom 15:4 \x*  
\v 17 Koatasitu etat n…ôhlan m…ôm…ô, kitat net…ôm r…ôha Uhg…®n, okotos nasitu…ôn rafin m…®n …ôh, k…ôn motuwa net…ômim it…ôm kot…®tun nol…ôn w…ôk m…®n rafin it…ôm kot…ôw…®r.   
\c 4  
\m
\v 1 Timoti, oek…ôn-ip…®n…ô n…ôghat…ôn keike kit k…ôm ik e n…®gan…ômt…® Uhg…®n ne Kristo Iesu it…ôm otakil nol…ôn r…ôha net…ômim rafin, net…ôm koat…ômeg…ôh ne net…ôm k…ômot…®m…®s, k…ôn oek…ôn-ip…®n…ô n…ôghat…ôn u m…ôto-inu in otuwa m…®n mat…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô. K…ôn in…ôh, iakat…ôk…ôike mat…ôn k…ôm ik m…ôm…ô,  
\v 2 …ôn-iar…ôp n…ôghat…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n, k…ôn …ôtul mat…®p o n…ôn-iar…ôp…ôn, nat …ôpnap…®n m…ôm…ô ot…®m…ôt…®g …ôm, o ti…ôk…®s. ∆èg-…ôtuat…®p-in nol…ôn r…ôha net…ômim, k…ôn …ôn-i…ôp nol…ôn rat m…®n, k…ôn m…®l…ôs-ip…ôr n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn r…ôha net…ômim, k…ôn nian natol w…ôk m…®n u, r…ôham n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn ot…ôk…ôike m…ôf…ôm…ôh, k…ôn r…ôham n…ôg…ôtun…ôn ot…ôk…ôike m…ôtuat…®p m…ôw…®r.  
\v 3 N…ôk…ôike mol n…ôhlan m…ôto-inu, nian it…ôm tatuwa, net…ômim ok…ôsotolkeike…ôn m…ôm…ô okot…ôt…ôl…®g-in n…ôghat…ôn pahrien. M…ôto ilat okotos i…ôg…ôtun p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n it…ôm okot…ôg…ôtun n…ôghat…ôn m…®n it…ôm ilat …ôm kotolkeike.\x - \xo 4:3 \xt 1 Tim 4:1 \x*  
\v 4 K…ôn ilat okot…ôuhlin mat…ôlg…®lat o n…ôt…ôl…®g-in…ôn n…ôghat…ôn pahrien, k…ôn motuw…®n moat…ôt…ôl…®g-in namsu eiueiu…ô m…®n.   
\p
\v 5 M…ôto ik, atehm w…®r r…ôham n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn ne r…ôham nol…ôn m…®n e nian m…®n rafin, nat …ôpnap…®n nat p…®s…®n p…®s…®n m…®n koatuwa e r…ôham n…ômeg…ôh…ôn, k…ôn …ôtul …ôskas…®k nian n…ôrat…ôn tatuwa, k…ôn uw…®n m…ôn-iar…ôp namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r, k…ôn ol rafin w…ôk it…ôm Uhg…®n t…ômos-ip…ôn k…ôm ik m…ôm…ô on…ôkol.   
\p
\v 6 Timoti, ol nat…®mnat m…®n …ôh, m…ôto-inu ot…ôsuw…ôh…ôn, io ek…®m…®s. K…ôn roiu n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhak tahmen e wain it…ôm k…®nat…ôht…ôg-p…ôn e olta m…ôm…ô okol sakrifais lan.\x - \xo 4:6 \xt Fil 2:17 \x*  
\v 7 E r…ôhak fait w…®r r…ôha nahat…ôt…ô…ôn, emat…®pin w…®r nelm…ôk, k…ôn e r…ôhak naiu…ôn, io emaiu w…®r r…ôk…®s m…ôtoarus-pa namnun naiu…ôn, k…ôn io ematask…ôl…®m w…®r nol…ôn …ôtuat…®p r…ôha nahat…ôt…ô…ôn k…ôn em…ôsap…ôs…ôn w…ôk r…ôha n…ôn-iar…ôp…ôn namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r.\x - \xo 4:7 \xt 1 Tim 6:12 \x*  
\v 8 K…ôn roiu, I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô it…ôm r…ôhan nakil…ôn t…ôtuat…®p w…®r, in t…ômol …ôpen-…ôpen…ô e n…ôtou…ôn r…ôhak, inu hat r…ôha et…ôm tatol win e r…ôhan naiu…ôn, k…ôn in ot…ôfauin-pa k…ôm io e nian r…ôha nakil…ôn m…ôto-inu in t…ômakil io m…ôm…ô r…ôhak n…ômeg…ôh…ôn t…ôtuat…®p. K…ôn s…ôn…ôm…ô io p…®s…®n …ôm, m…ôto otos-ip…ôn k…ôm net…ômim rafin it…ôm kotolkeike moat…ôsahgin m…ôm…ô in otuwa m…®n.\x - \xo 4:8 \xt 1 Kor 9:24-25 \x*\fig |alt="man wearing wreath" src="BK00157B.TIF" size="col" loc="2Ti 4:8" ref="2 Tim 4:8" \fig*   
\s1 Pol t…ôm…ôn-iar…ôp namnus…ôn r…ôha in m…®n neen  
\p
\v 9 Eam-in u…ôhai …ôm r…ôham suat…®p m…ôm…ô on…ôkuwa mehm io,  
\v 10 m…ôto-inu Temas, u tolkeike p…®k n…ôtueint…ôn u, in t…ômap…ôs io maiu muw…®n Tesalonaeka. Kresens t…®nuw…®n r…ôk…®s …ôp…ôh Kalesia, k…ôn Taetas t…®nuw…®n r…ôk…®s Talmesia.  
\v 11 M…ôto Luk p…®s…®n …ôm it…®mlau min. T…ôw…®r m…ôm…ô nian nakatuwa, onakit Mak it…ômlau min, m…ôto-inu in t…®tun nasitu…ôn e w…ôk r…ôhak.\x - \xo 4:11 \xt W…ôk 15:37-39; 2 Kor 8:23; Kol 4:14 \x*  
\v 12 Emahl-ip…ôn r…ôk…®s Tikikas tuw…®n …ôp…ôh Efesas.  
\v 13 K…ôn nian nakatuwa, onakos r…ôhak kot it…ôm em…ôl…ôh…ôu k…ôm Kapas …ôp…ôh Troas, k…ôn onakos m…®n r…ôhak naoa m…®n it…ôm k…ômaiu-aiu, k…ôn iakolkeike p…®k m…®n m…ôm…ô onakos naoa m…®n u k…ômol e nuwig…® sipsip.\x - \xo 4:13 \xt W…ôk 20:6 \x*\fig |alt="scrolls, pen, inkwell" src="HK00153B.TIF" size="col" loc="2Ti 4:13" ref="2 Tim 4:13" \fig*   
\p
\v 14 Suah u Aleksanta it…ôm et…ômim r…ôha nol…ôn w…ôk e iaen, in t…ômatol t…ôrat k…ôm io. I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô otos-ip…ôn n…®tai n…ôtou…ôn r…ôhan o nat…®mnat m…®n …ôh.\x - \xo 4:14 \xt Aes 59:18; Rom 2:6 \x*  
\v 15 K…ôn ik m…®n, at…ôto ik o suah …ôh, m…ôto-inu t…ôtahtos…®g-in n…ôghat…ôn m…®n r…ôhatat.   
\p
\v 16 Nian emaup…ôn m…ôtul e kot m…ôm…ô ek…ôn-iar…ôp n…ôghat…ôn m…®n r…ôhak, suah kit t…ôm…ôs…ôtul-ar…ôp…ôn masitu lak, m…ôto net…ômim rafin k…ômotag…®m motap…ôs io. P…ôs Uhg…®n n…®kin ot…ôs…ôht…ôn nat…®mnat rafin it…ôm ilat k…ômoatol.  
\v 17 M…ôto I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô t…ôm…ôtul e n…®kal…®k mos-ipa n…ôsan…ôn…ôn k…ôm io m…ôm…ô ek…ôn-iar…ôp w…®r n…ôghat…ôn r…ôhan, k…ôn p…ôs Iaihlu…ô m…®n okot…ôto. K…ôn t…ôm…®l…ôs-iar…ôp io e nohl…® laion.  
\v 18 I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô ot…®l…ôs-ir…ôk…®s io e n…ôrat…ôn m…®n rafin it…ôm okol k…ôm io, k…ôn in otask…ôl…®m w…®r io, k…ôn m…®l…ôs io ekuw…®n e n…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô…ôn r…ôhan …ôp…ôh il…®s e nego e neai. P…ôs kot…®l…ôs-ip…ôr n…ôrg…®n tatuw…®n matuw…®n namnun t…®k…ô. ∆èw…ôh.   
\s1 Namnun n…ôghat…ôn  
\p
\v 19 Iat…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm Prisila ne Akwila, ne Onesiforas ne r…ôhan m…®n.\x - \xo 4:19 \xt W…ôk 18:2; 2 Tim 1:16-17 \x*  
\v 20 Erastas t…ôm…ôs…ôt…ôu-pa-m…ôn io, in …ôp…ôh Korin. K…ôn nian emiet Maelitas, emap…ôs Trofimas t…ôtat…®g m…ôto-inu in tat…®m…®s.\x - \xo 4:20 \xt W…ôk 19:22; 20:4; Rom 16:23 \x*  
\v 21 Alkut p…®k m…ôm…ô nakuwa u…ôhai …ôm ik…®n-u, uaris…®g in nian r…ôha n…ôt…ôp…ôn. Iupulas tat…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm ik, k…ôn Putens, ne Linus, ne Klotia, ne pi…ôtat m…®n rafin ik…®n-u koat…ôn t…ôw…®r k…ôm ik.   
\p
\v 22 P…ôs I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô t…ôtat…®g it…ômat min. P…ôs Uhg…®n otawte-in r…ôhan n…ôw…®r…ôn k…ôm ik.   